    <h1>Dynamic Ads</h1>
    <p class="description"><strong>Dynamic ads</strong> are personalised advertisements that automatically generate creative from a product catalog based on each viewer's browsing behaviour, interests, or past purchases. Meta reports dynamic ads drive <strong>34% lower cost per acquisition</strong> compared to static ads. They are the default retargeting format for ecommerce brands with 20+ products.</p>
