            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Meta (Facebook + Instagram), Google (Performance Max and Dynamic Remarketing), TikTok, Pinterest, and Snapchat all offer dynamic ad formats. Meta DPA and Google Performance Max are the most widely adopted.</p></div></div>
          </div>
