            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Dynamic ads personalise creative per individual based on their browsing behaviour, showing each person different products. Custom-audience retargeting shows the same creative to everyone in the audience.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
